import { CardMedia, Container, Grid, Typography, Card, Avatar, CardContent, Button } from "@material-ui/core";
import React from "react";
import useStyles from "../../theme/useStyles";

const Productos = () => {
    const classes = useStyles();
    return(
        <Container className={classes.containermt}>
            <Typography variant="h4" className={classes.text_title}>
                Productos
            </Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={4}>
                <Grid item lg={3} md={4} sm={6} xs={12}>
                    <Card>
                        <CardMedia
                            className={classes.media}
                            image="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.aeTdOU0yTCVAQ2ORxt5uQAHaHa?pid=ImgDet&rs=1"
                            title="mi producto"
                        >
                            <Avatar 
                                variant="square"
                                className={classes.price}
                            >
                                $9.99
                            </Avatar>
                        </CardMedia>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography 
                                variant="h6"
                                className={classes.text_card}
                            >
                                Zapato Cafe SampleBrand
                            </Typography>
                            <Button 
                                variant="contained" 
                                color="primary"
                                fullWidth
                            >
                                Mas Detalles
                            </Button>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
};

export default Productos;
